At Mighty Spark we make healthy protein taste delicious. Our flavorful options make mealtime a whole lot easier by removing the mealtime prep work for you because of the whole-food ingredients we add to our premium cuts of all-natural poultry.

Choose from flavors like Bruschetta Chicken, Fajita Seasoned Chicken, Spinach & Feta Chicken, Queso Fresco & Jalapeño Turkey, Bacon-Bursting Turkey + more!

More Flavor, More Protein, Less Calories, Less Time Meal Prepping😇

Mighty Spark’s all-natural chicken and turkey is sourced from U.S. farms, made with premium cuts, has no added hormones and is blended with whole-food ingredients. The result is a protein-packed powerhouse of flavor, without the time required for meal prep. Forget about bland, flavorless chicken breasts and get excited about bringing more to the table!🍽
